18 the asphalt mixture meets the established performance criteria. The Transportation
19 Cabinet shall report on the percentage of recycled asphalt products used in state projects
20 to the Interim Joint Committee on Appropriations and Revenue on or before November 1,
21 2027. It is the intent of the General Assembly that by 2030, the Transportation Cabinet
22 shall use an asphalt mixture that utilizes 30 percent or greater recycled asphalt products.
